=====
[[include :scp-wiki:component:preview
text=Case File "Faultline"]]
=====

[[div style="display: none;"]]
[[include component:image-block name=https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/uiu-file-1972-055/FBI%20UIU%20Crest|caption=.]]
[[/div]]

